data.description: Nice rock home on .5 acre lot on paved Turner road that is move in ready.  This home features 3 bed 2 bath with open concept living and kitchen - Beautifully updated kitchen with granite counter tops, large center island - updated bathroom with beautiful walk in shower, large yard plus a 2 car covered carport.  Come check out this great home before it is gone!
